Class AbstractRexslMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • com.rexsl.maven.AbstractRexslMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextEnabled, Mojo, Contextualizable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CheckMojo, PackageMojo, RunMojo

    public abstract class AbstractRexslMojo
extends AbstractMojo
implements Contextualizable
    Abstract mojo.

    We import StaticLoggerBinder from SLF4J package, but this class actually is not from slf4j artifact. Instead, we are using com.rempl.plugins:rempl-maven-plugin artifact, where this class is defined. Additional information about how exactly this reloading works can be found at SLF4J documentation. This implementation of StaticLoggerBinder forwards all SLF4J calls to Maven log.

    This class is public because Maven needs it this way.

    The class is NOT thread-safe.

    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Yegor Bugayenko (yegor@tpc2.com)
